lead_paragraph: The true value of Arsenal's table-topping display against Basel will not become clear until Monday's draw for the Champions League last 16 but a 4-1 win proved they are starting to punch their weight again in the competition.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Punching Their Weight Again in Europe
